description:
I just want to start by saying that doing a Serviced video with Moses was like dealing with a hair-trigger loaded gun- or maybe I should say rifle, with his big equipment!
Right from the outset he was ready to pop. You can tell I am barely stroking him and only able to really blow him for 10-20 seconds at a time. It's VERY hot just how turned on he is.
It's been a while since his solo aired, and I had intended on getting Moses back to do some work with other models. He was ready to go during March, but everyone was preparing for Spring break (or gone) so I figured I would keep him busy doing a Serviced video.
You guys really sent some positive comments about him. I was concerned that his long hair might not go over well, but between his Serviced video and the great feedback I had on him, I am bound and determined to get him in with another model.
I think he would look great with Teo, so I think I will try to make that happen first.
But for this video, you can't beat how arousing this video is!
title: Bryan & Moses - Serviced
